	<span style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><a name="IntroducingBEACONAMAManagedSolution" style="color:#0000FF!important;"></a>Release of BEACON Advanced Metering Analytics Managed Solution Widens Badger Meter </span></span></strong></span></div>
