	<div>
		<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
			<img src="http://www.badgermeter.com/Badger-Files/Images/Gas-Utility/BEACON/BEACON_globe_monitor_tablet_smartphone.jpg" style="font-family: verdana,geneva,sans-serif; width: 156px; margin: 0px; border: 0px solid #000000; height: 112px; float: right;" align="right" width="156" height="112"></p>
		<div>
			<span style="font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">We are proud to introduce our new end-to-end managed solution for water utility management, BEACON Advanced Metering Analytics (AMA). BEACON AMA combines the intuitive BEACON AMA software suite with proven ORION<span style="font-size:7px;"><sup>&reg;</sup></span> Advanced Metering Infrastructure (AMI) technology, using fixed and cellular networks to give utilities greater control, more information and enhanced customer service. Built-in infrastructure management services and supplied endpoint upgrades eliminate maintenance and technology concerns. Consumer engagement tools help enhance customer service, increase customer satisfaction and reduce costs.&nbsp;</span></div>
	</div>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		&nbsp;</p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">With the release of BEACON AMA, Badger Meter also </span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">becomes the first major water meter company to </span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">release a cost-effective cellular based solution for </span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">system-wide deployment.</span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		&nbsp;</p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">BEACON AMA gives you a powerful solution for any&nbsp;water </span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">utility customer looking for the benefits of fixed&nbsp;network&nbsp;</span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">and analytics, but also wanting the convenience of a </span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">managed solution.</span></p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		&nbsp;</p>
	<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
		<span style="font-family:verdana,geneva,sans-serif;">To support sales efforts, starting in February, BEACON AMA will be promoted with a fully integrated campaign, including print and online advertising, public relations, and trade show and conference promotion.</span></p>
